This is a 31 minute workout called '30 min Full Body Fat Loss Standing Workout (No Jumping) | Quiet Cardio, No Yoga Mat Needed ~ Emi' from the channel emi wong.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
